                <h5>February 2, 2019</h5>
                <img src="images/Marathon.jpeg" class="img-fluid" style="width:50%"></img>
                </a>
                <p style="margin-top:25px">It’s been quite a journey, since I started my Full Stack Web Development apprenticeship through Bloc with zero programming experience. I have made lots of research prior to entering this field and it became evident to me that programming is really for people who have the stamina and patience to sit down and simply just learn.</p>
                <p>
                <button class="btn button" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseArticle2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseArticle2">
