                  <p style="margin-top:25px">It has been a while since I have posted my last story, but the past 2 months have been wild. Lots of this.props, this.state, debugging, sweat and long nights. Just to recap quickly, I started with zero knowledge when it comes to programming and within 5–10 weeks into Bloc’s Full Stack Web Development Program, I was able to create a music player app and a chat app. It felt super rewarding implementing the skills I learned to create real applications.</p>
                  <p>
